## Architecture

The admin panel is a separate Vite SPA deployed to Cloudflare Pages. It talks to the Worker via `/admin/*` API routes. The Worker handles auth (JWT), tenant CRUD, and serves tenant config to the checkout.

### New Worker routes needed

```
POST   /admin/auth/register     - create tenant account
POST   /admin/auth/login        - login, return JWT
POST   /admin/auth/logout       - invalidate token
GET    /admin/tenant             - get full tenant config (auth required)
PUT    /admin/tenant             - update tenant config (auth required)
PUT    /admin/tenant/brp        - update BRP credentials + validate (auth required)
PUT    /admin/tenant/branding   - update branding only (auth required)
PUT    /admin/tenant/products   - update product display settings (auth required)
PUT    /admin/tenant/domain     - set custom domain (auth required)
